		ren (mv001 mv002 mv003 sm101e1 sm500c1 sm862a sm101e2 sm500c2 sm862b sm836 sm838a) (v001 v002 v003 s101e1 s600ca s1056a s101e2 s600cb s1056b s1033 s1035a)
